com.skysql.monitor
Class monitor

java.lang.Object
  com.skysql.monitor.monitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
commandMonitor, crmMonitor, deltaMonitor, globalMonitor, nodeStateMonitor, pingMonitor
public class monitor
extends java.lang.Object

The base monitor class, it is from this class that all monitors are derived. The monitor class provides an SQL monitor that executes a SQL statement on the monitored database, this statement returns a single row and single column result set that is the value of the monitor.

Author:
Mark Riddoch
